348
00:20:41,578 --> 00:20:46,378
Mereka ingin mengkonfirmasi isinya secepat mungkin.

349
00:20:46,378 --> 00:20:47,878
Apa aku salah?

350
00:20:50,478 --> 00:20:51,478
